(firstQuint)High Dose Camptothecin-11 (CPT-11) in Recurrent Unresectable Malignant Glioma.

 This is a phase I/II study of high dose irinotecan in patients with recurrent unresectable malignant glioma on steroids/anti-epileptics.

 The purpose is to compare the response to treatment and side effects associated with high dose irinotecan in patients with recurrent brain tumors.

